      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@\n+created: 2025-12-11\n+title: Tenzir Changelog v0.11.1\n+intro: >-\n+  This patch release improves the CLI display with better card view styling and author\n+  formatting. The card view now displays type-colored borders and properly formats\n+  non-GitHub authors without the @ prefix for improved readability."
    },
